ul.li: Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-EntityCode where concept is-a COMPPKG

description.value: A container intended to contain sufficient material for more than one use, but grouped or organized to provide individual access to sufficient material for a single use. Often used to ensure that the proper type and amount of material is consumed/expended for each use.
